verbose_text: This strategy identified four cis G x BMI variants (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY), one of which, rs3851570 (cis G x BMI interaction on ALG9 expression [MIM : 606941], p value = 2.0 x 10 -8), is associated with 53 genes in trans (Bonferroni corrected p value threshold of p < 1.1 x 10 -7) (XREF_FIG A, XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY, XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
